Author: lunaticleg
Text: I know what you're feeling, but you just need to know that you're probably much thinner than you think...that's just body dysmorphia telling you that you're fat. Your mom might have thinner legs at your same weight because maybe she has a different body shape and different fat distribution than you.

Author: janescandycanes
Text: it’s your dysmorphia. there’s no way you didn’t lose weight after 2 months of restricting.
